{"tid":586994,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TVB 洩密？ 42歲湯盈盈疑再度懷孕陀第三胎","createTime":"2018-03-10T04:55:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-10T10:59:12.000Z","uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"14ec20eaad0a8155d89b55f8485e2c7faf836fa9","tid":586994,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T04:55:47.000Z","msg":"52歲藝人錢嘉樂與42歲湯盈盈結婚五年，先後誕下大女Alyssa及細女Kassidy，一家四口幸福美滿。早前有傳兩人想追第三胎，更有指盈盈已經成功佗B，但其後否認傳聞，仲笑言自己只係肥咗，係一個美麗嘅誤會，點知近日再度傳出盈盈有喜嘅消息！ <br />\n<br />\n事緣TVB社交網專頁尋日上載咗一段盈盈同Kassidy做手作嘅短片，但標題竟然寫住「恭喜湯盈盈再度懷孕！」疑洩密喜訊引起網上熱議。不過，該專頁已經刪除有關標題，換上「湯盈盈親子速遞」標題，仲留言話：「大家姐嘅囡囡Alyssa（錢凱晴）同Kassidy（錢凱琪）應該都好期待有其他兄弟姊妹喇～」究竟內情係點？真係令人摸不着頭腦呀！"},{"pid":"8c26f6a2ddbd2b2e492854b702f6affb666ad600","tid":586994,"uid":94551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T04:59:12.000Z","msg":"連登之女"},{"pid":"defce1f4c8099d357b83cecd9a8dfb78ba1b91f2","tid":586994,"uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T05:00:05.000Z","msg":"主動騎乘"},{"pid":"eed245da05aeda4209c6abd85e821486209c32d9","tid":586994,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T05:02:02.000Z","msg":"未夠三個月？"},{"pid":"544c5ed59372051e2504f3b2a0230b385e929427","tid":586994,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T05:17:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 家姐"},{"pid":"c470cec1dddd152fd6448a056101757b0676e74d","tid":586994,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T05:21:24.000Z","msg":"呢個會唔會係最靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa26cbd60a703b2ba7884eb872e5569b865b9044","tid":586994,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c470cec1dddd152fd6448a056101757b0676e74d","tid":586994,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T05:21:24.000Z","msg":"呢個會唔會係最靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgm